Package: ptfs4br
Title: Pedotransfer Functions for Soil Applications in the Brazilian Territory
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2020-04-03
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alessandro",
           family = "Samuel-Rosa",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alessandrorosa@utfpr.edu.br",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0877-1320"))
Description: Collection of pedotransfer functions (PTFs), i.e. statistical models for predicting soil 
   properties, built using open legacy data collected in the Brazilian territory. Present version contains PTFs
   for predicting carbon and organic matter content.
Imports:
   shiny
